Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw growled. She hadn't nabbed a Predacon that could lead to 
Megatron's whereabouts. He lowered herself to the ground and walked slowly 
towards the Arc. She hated to think that she had to see the Maximals again. 
She felt it was wrong to be near them.

As she walked, she saw three bots positioned near the Arc. She growled and 
paused. Her scanners picked them up as Predacons. She walked towards Black 
Arachnia and Inferno. Rampage wasn't too far. She made sure that she could 
see him. She came up a few feet away from them, and said, "You there, who 
are you?"
